---


<Header title="Business Intelligence & Analytics for Better Decisions" description="Unlock data-driven insights with business intelligence and analytics, empowering informed decision-making and growth." canonical={ currentUrl }>
	<style>
        .service_shrt {
            font-family: Instrument Sans;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 28.8px;
            color: #FFFFFFCC;
        }
		.home_title{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
            font-size: 75px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 96px;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            text-align: left;
			color: white;
		}
		.site-title-layer {
			background-size: cover;
			background-color: #000000;
		}
		.home_description{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 28.8px;
            text-align: left;
			color: #FFFFFFCC;
		}
		.contract{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 18px;
			font-weight: 500;
			line-height: 20px;
			text-align: left;
			color: #000000CC;
		}

        /* services */
        .services{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 40px;
			font-weight: 600;
			line-height: 48px;
			letter-spacing: -0.03em;
			text-align: left;
			color: #000000;
		}
		.services-title{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 24px;
			font-weight: 500;
			line-height: 38.4px;
			text-align: left;
		}
		.services-description{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 15px;
			font-weight: 500;
			line-height: 24px;
			text-align: left;
		}

		/* image section */
		.list_element{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 20px;
			font-weight: 500;
			line-height: 32px;
			text-align: left;
			color: #000000;
		}
		.capabilities{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 16px;
			font-weight: 500;
			line-height: 25.6px;
			text-align: left;
			color: #006B9E;
		}

		/* services scroll section */
		.h2{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 36px;
			font-weight: 600;
			line-height: 43.2px;
			letter-spacing: -0.03em;
			text-align: left;
			color: #FFFFFF;
		}

		.diff-description{
			font-family: Instrument Sans;
			font-size: 16px;
			font-weight: 500;
			line-height: 25.6px;
			text-align: left;
			color: #FFFFFFCC;
		}



		@media (max-width: 600px) {
			.post{
				width: 100%;
			}
			.post_title{
				font-size: 24px;
			}
			.blogs-title{
				font-size: 32px;
			}
			.blogMain{
				background-color: #292d6b;
				color: white;
			}
			.site-title-layer::before{
				height: 435px;
			}
            .home_title{
                font-size: 44px;
                line-height:60.8px;
            }
		}
	</style>
	<header class="">
		<Nav />
		<div class="px-8 lg:px-12 py-12 site-title-layer overflow-hidden relative flex items-start" >
			<div class="header flex flex-col items-start justify-start border-[#FFFFFF33]">
                <h6 class="service_shrt text-start mb-5">
                    SERVICES
                </h6>
				<h1 class="home_title text-start">
					Business Intelligence / Analytics
				</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
		<section>
			<div class="relative pb-16 bg-black">
                <img src="/new_services/services3.webp" width="100%" height="500px" alt="airline" />
            </div>

			<!-- services -->
			<div class="lg:pl-12 pl-8 pr-8 lg:pb-28 lg:pr-40 bg-black">
				<div class="inner-layer lg:pb-0 pb-8 lg:gap-24">
					<div class="">
                        <div class="">
                            <div class="diff-description pb-8">The top concern for industries today is managing a growing volume of structured and unstructured data, avoiding process delays anddata compliance issues. As the economic tide changes, opportunities do come, and organizations position themselves to capitalize on these opportunities. Business Intelligence solutions are expected to accelerate business growth by enabling faster, more accurate decisions. It is supposed to reduce time-to-market. Organizations expect a culture of innovation through access to right information at the right time. You use business intelligence for various purposes but one prominent reason amongst them is a creation of new business models.</div>
